  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "Eric was camping in the Patrick’s creek campground of Del Norte County Ca. He had been camping since Thursday 9/12/2024. His last contact was at 7:57 pm on 9/16/2024. He is very familiar with the area. His family checked on him in 9/18/2024 and he was not there his truck, dogs, cat, money and phone a long with his personal items were there. His camp was not disturbed. No signs of struggle, blood etc. he vanished without a trace. Search and rescue are still working the remote area."^^xsd:String;
  mpr:columnURI "https://www.namus.gov/MissingPersons/Case#/130137?nav"^^xsd:String;
  mpr:hasImageURL "https://www.namus.gov/api/CaseSets/NamUs/MissingPersons/Cases/130137/Images/211490/Thumbnail"^^xsd:String .

