  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "Michael is currently driving (and living out of) a 1995 Chevy van bearing CA. The van is tan/brown in color with a pop-up top and silver ladder on the rear. On 7/31/24, family saw Michael at the Greenville Campground in Plumas County. Michael is from Greenville, but during a text message exchange with family on 08/01/2024, he said he was in the Beckwourth area and may travel to Frenchman Lake Plumas County. Family has not seen or heard from Michael since the text message exchange on 08/01/2024."^^xsd:String;
  mpr:columnURI "https://www.namus.gov/MissingPersons/Case#/128017?nav"^^xsd:String;
  mpr:hasImageURL "https://www.namus.gov/api/CaseSets/NamUs/MissingPersons/Cases/128017/Images/209510/Thumbnail"^^xsd:String .

