  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "Raneisha Williams was on a court ordered stay at Solano House - Yolo Community Care Continuum in Fairfield, CA. On 7/24/24 at approximately 1300 hours, Solano House staff gave Ms. Williams a 1-hour pass to go to the McDonald's located at 699 Beck Ave, Fairfield, CA. When Solano House staff returned at the appointed time to retrieve Ms. Williams, she was not there. Prior to moving into Solano House, Ms. Williams had been living unhoused in Vallejo, CA. She was photographed at the DMV office in Fairfield on 07/25/2024, the same day and prior to going missing."^^xsd:String;
  mpr:columnURI "https://www.namus.gov/MissingPersons/Case#/131037?nav"^^xsd:String;
  mpr:hasImageURL "https://www.namus.gov/api/CaseSets/NamUs/MissingPersons/Cases/131037/Images/210844/Thumbnail"^^xsd:String .

