  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "Stehpanie and her husband (MP127378) were last contacted on or about July 16, 2024. Stephanie worked from home and logged into work from a laptop computer. She last logged in on July 16, 2024. Following July 16, 2024, Stephanie and her husband have not been heard from or seen since. A review of their known fianancial accounts shows no activitiy. The cell phones belonging to both parties were also left at the residence as was their only vehicle."^^xsd:String;
  mpr:columnURI "https://www.namus.gov/MissingPersons/Case#/127384?nav"^^xsd:String;
