  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "Iit is believed Jose and his wife (MP127384) were last contacted at their apartment located in the City of Simi Valley on July 16, 2024. Jose's wife stopped logging into her work computer for work on July 16, 2024. After not logging in for approximately a week, Her employer contacted an emergency contact, who then contacted the Simi Valley Police Department. Both have not been seen or heard from since. The apartment was searched and two cell phones were located, hand written wills were also located. A review of their financial records shows no activity following July 16, 2024."^^xsd:String;
  mpr:columnURI "https://www.namus.gov/MissingPersons/Case#/127378?nav"^^xsd:String;
  mpr:hasImageURL "https://www.namus.gov/api/CaseSets/NamUs/MissingPersons/Cases/127378/Images/Default/Thumbnail"^^xsd:String .

