  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "On 5/5/24 at 2330 hours PST, Emmanuel Zatarain was last seen at the residence and had not been seen since at the time of the original report 5/7/24. Emmanuel Zatarain left behind his phone, vehicle, and all associated documents. Friends believe that Emmanuel Zatarain is with someone in the area of \"Escuela Popular\" in San Jose. Emmanuel Zatarain returned home briefly on 5/8/24 at 0530 hours PST and then left before he could be located. Due to the unusual relationship of Emmanuel Zatarain and the associated he is possibly with, Emmanuel's case will remain active until he can be contacted by law enforcement and interviewed to ensure he is not the victim of a crime."^^xsd:String;
  mpr:columnURI "https://www.namus.gov/MissingPersons/Case#/121733?nav"^^xsd:String;
  mpr:hasImageURL "https://www.namus.gov/api/CaseSets/NamUs/MissingPersons/Cases/121733/Images/204061/Thumbnail"^^xsd:String .

