  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "Rocco was last seen at his home in Santa Maria, CA. by his landlord on the night of April 26th 2024. His vehicle was seen later that night eastbound on the north end of the city through a License Plate Reader database. His vehicle was subsequently found abandoned in the bushes at the intersection of Callender Road and Highway One near Oceano, CA. It appeared that the vehicle was involved in a single vehicle collision after a tire blow out."^^xsd:String;
