  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "Anthony Evans, age 35, was last seen 12/15/2023 by family members near Mohawk Vista Rd. approximately 5 miles west of the City of Portola and was reported missing two days later. Plumas County Search and Rescue personnel as well as family and friends extensively searched the remote wooded area near a family members residence, where Anthony was believed to have traveled on foot. The search continued until winter weather hampered their efforts. Anthony has not been seen or heard from since."^^xsd:String;
