  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "On 10/12/2023, Missing Person (MP) was found by LAPD and taken to Glendora Hospital by the Los Angeles Fire Department to receive treatment for ongoing medical issues. PR was called and met MP at the hospital. MP asked the PR for a drink while at the hospital. The PR went a got a soda for MP and when he returned, PR discovered that MP had left. The PR checked the area but did not find MP. MP has gone missing 6 - 7 times previously."^^xsd:String;
  mpr:columnURI "https://www.namus.gov/MissingPersons/Case#/116476?nav"^^xsd:String;
