  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance """Yuri had plans to relocate to Michigan and seek a new job and settlement.
He discussed these plans with family members. He also spoke about touring the US playing at dive bars, as he is an accomplished guitar player. He was last seen by his sister April 6 after taking an Uber to a nearby Vons. He did not contact family, friends or others to notify them of his whereabouts after this. He also left behind his as personal affects, credit cards, etc."""^^xsd:String;
  mpr:columnURI "https://www.namus.gov/MissingPersons/Case#/90690?nav"^^xsd:String;
  mpr:hasImageURL "https://www.namus.gov/api/CaseSets/NamUs/MissingPersons/Cases/90690/Images/173333/Thumbnail"^^xsd:String .

