  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "Jose Zamora left his residence in Anaheim on 8-24-21, after a property eviction and he boarded a bus to Mexico. Zamora has lived in Anaheim for about 40 years. From the Tijuana airport, he was expected to fly to Morelia, Michoacan. Zamora missed his flight and remained in Tijuana. Law enforcement sources showed he returned to USA at the San Ysidro, CA port of entry on 8-25-21. He has not been seen or heard from since this trip and his family is looking for him."^^xsd:String;
