  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "MP is a former transient who was in a program to help him, including finding him a place to stay. He was at the above address in San Leandro, CA until that date. He was behind in rent and failed to check in with his case worker, Geneva Long (glong@bfwc.org. There has been no contact since then and he does not answer his cell phone."^^xsd:String;
