  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "MP left her home after a disagreement with her mother. MP then ran away after going to school on 22APR19. MP was thought to be staying with a friend from her High School but has not contacted the friend for over 4 days. MP is believed to be couch surfing and wandering during the day. High School administrators are aware of the situation and have been attempting to locate MP and connect her with her mother."^^xsd:String;
