  rdfs:hasMapData </ser531/ontologies/MissingPersonReport#http%3A//www.google.com/maps/place/37.8134679%2C-122.307917>;
  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance """LEVICOFF was last seen on 21Sep18 at approx. 0500 hrs. at her residence by her roommates / landlords. It is
unknown what LEVICOFF was wearing when she was last seen. A three page suicide note was found in her
room by her roommates / landlords when they went to check on her.

LEVICOFF's cell phone was last pinged on 24Sep18 at approx. 0644 hrs. in the area of 1255 Armstead Rd.,
San Francisco.

At the time of this flier, LEVICOFF's vehicle was located in the area of 6302 Merchant Rd. San Francisco. The
vehicle was unoccupied at this time."""^^xsd:String;
  mpr:columnURI "https://www.namus.gov/MissingPersons/Case#/52994?nav"^^xsd:String;
