  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "On July 26th, 2018 Javier Jimenez Hernandez was involved in a hit & run collision on the Eastbound 118 freeway and Kuehner Drive in Simi Valley around 9:30pm or 10:30pm. His vehicle was located with damage & abandoned about five miles away from where the collision took place near a trail head/fire access road entrance between Cottonwood Drive & Yosemite Ave. Javier may have been on foot on streets named Evening Sky Drive and Yosemite Avenue. Javier has had no contact with friends or family since his disappearance."^^xsd:String;
