  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "Joshua Chamberlain Coe has gone missing from the Auburn CA area. Joshua was last seen on December 7th when his mother dropped him off in the city of Auburn. There has been no contact with family, friends or social media contacts. Josh has been a known transient in the Placer and Nevada County areas. The Placer County Sheriff's office is seeking any information as to his whereabouts or last known location. Please contact Detective Jeff Martin at 530-889-6984 or Detective Daniel Meier at 530-889-7855."^^xsd:String;
  mpr:columnURI "https://www.namus.gov/MissingPersons/Case#/43237?nav"^^xsd:String;
  mpr:hasImageURL "https://www.namus.gov/api/CaseSets/NamUs/MissingPersons/Cases/43237/Images/71481/Thumbnail"^^xsd:String .

