  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "On the morning of 9-29-17 at approximately 0800 hours., Jonathan Jimenez went to work and never returned home. Jonathan texted his sister after work at approximately 1800 hours and told her he was on his way home but did not return. On 9-29-17 at approximately 2300 hours, Jonathan texted her again and told her he was on his way home, however never returned. He has not been heard from or seen since."^^xsd:String;
