  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "The reporting party has not had contact with Joelle since July 2016. Family and friends have told the reporting party they last had contact with Joelle in March 2017 when she was in Tecate, Mexico. Joelle's daughter shared that Joelle was supposed to meet her boyfriend, Jose Gonzales (NFD), at a strip club to cross the border into Mexico but has not heard from Joelle since then (unknown date and location). Joelle's daughter has received social media messages from Jose telling her Joelle is dead in Mexico."^^xsd:String;
