  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "On 03/02/17 Dwight Meier mailed a letter to his parents stating that he would no longer see them. The letter was not received until 03/05/17. When the letter was received, his parents contacted the police and filed a missing person report. Meier's vehicle was located at Walmart in Livermore on 03/05/17, but Dwight Meier's whereabouts are unknown. LPD Officers checked Meier's residence and the area around the Livermore Walmart, but they have not located Dwight Meier."^^xsd:String;
