  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "Jeremy Tyler Howard was last seen in the early morning of Thursday December 24, 2015. Howard went missing near La Jolla Cove in San Diego. He is described as a 19 year old black, male, 6’04” to 6’05”, 175-180 LBS, short curly tapered line-up hair, brown eyes, with fuzz like facial hair. Howard was last seen wearing a maroon shirt, black sweat pants and no shoes. Howard has a tattoo on his right forearm of a cross with “faith” written above it. He also has the name “Rhashea” and 07/05/07 tattooed on his left forearm. Howard has a scar on the left side of his lip with possible stitches"^^xsd:String;
  mpr:columnURI "https://www.namus.gov/MissingPersons/Case#/33549?nav"^^xsd:String;
