  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance """He was last seen on April 21, 2013, leaving his residence in Dana Point, California where he recently rented a room two weeks prior. It was believed he was going to Tijuana, Mexico for dental work and has not been seen or heard from since. His vehicle Located in a long term parking lot in San Diego County near the Mexican Border.

His Family members are concerned that he may have met with foul play due to his lack of contact with family and friends."""^^xsd:String;
