  rdfs:hasMapData </ser531/ontologies/MissingPersonReport#http%3A//www.google.com/maps/place/37.1305012%2C-121.6543901>;
  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance """Sierra was last seen on the morning of Friday, 03/16/12 by her mother as she was getting ready for
school. Sierra attends Sobrato HS in Morgan Hill, CA. A school friend stated she communicated with
Sierra via text message on Friday 3/16/12 at approximately 0711 hours to meet before class started
to discuss homework. Sierra never made that meeting. Sierra also did not board the school bus she
takes everyday which picks her up at 0735 hrs. Sierra was also absent from school all day, Friday
3/16/12. Many of her friends have been contacted by telephone and on Facebook to notify them
Sierra has been reported as a missing person. Sierra has never been a run away before and has not
had any recent events in her life that would indicate she wanted to leave voluntarily.
Sierra grew up in the city of Fremont, California, where she attended grade schools and some high
school prior to moving to Morgan Hill, California. Friends and family from the Fremont area have
also been notified Sierra is missing, as well as Fremont Police Dept."""^^xsd:String;
  mpr:columnURI "https://www.namus.gov/MissingPersons/Case#/14258?nav"^^xsd:String;
  mpr:hasImageURL "https://www.namus.gov/api/CaseSets/NamUs/MissingPersons/Cases/14258/Images/63223/Thumbnail"^^xsd:String .

