  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance """Kevin drove from Miami, FL to Los Angeles, CA. He was planning on returning the vehicle to the dealership in Los Angeles.

He purchased a new iPhone from AT&T in Sherman Oaks on 11/5/11 and sent everybody a message on Facebook asking for their contact information since he had a new phone.

He was supposed to go to a concert at Beyond the Stars Palace on 417 1/2 NW Brand Ave, Glendale, CA 91203 on 11/9/11 - we do not know if he made it there or not."""^^xsd:String;
  mpr:columnURI "https://www.namus.gov/MissingPersons/Case#/13266?nav"^^xsd:String;
  mpr:hasImageURL "https://www.namus.gov/api/CaseSets/NamUs/MissingPersons/Cases/13266/Images/48651/Thumbnail"^^xsd:String .

