  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "Loren left his home about 4:30 in the afternoon on October 15, 2010. On October 24, 2010 his 2001 Dodge Quad Cab truck was found in a remote area. His keys and wallet were in the truck. Search and Rescue looked for 9 days with dogs and never found a trace. 8 days after the truck was taken home a gun was found in it. He is a dedicated husband and father of two."^^xsd:String;
