  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "Willie was a transient who was last seen at the Del Taco at Highway 111 and Oasis Street, in Indio. He was originally from the city of Blythe and most recently he was staying at the Coachella Valley Rescue Mission. Willie's transient friend reported him missing when he was unable to locate Willie and he was unable to find him at the mission. A female later called and stated she was Willie's sister and she wanted to be contacted first, however that information was not confirmed. Willie's mother, father and brother are deceased."^^xsd:String;
