  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "The PR (father) reported that he went to Iran on vacation for a month. The PR left his house under the care of both of his sons, Mohammad Shirazi (MP) and Hossein Shirazi. The PR returned home and did not locate the MP. Through the investigation, biological evidence (blood) was located in the rug of the living room and and other furniture. This was treated as a no body homicide case. Hossein was subsequently arrested and convicted."^^xsd:String;
  mpr:columnURI "https://www.namus.gov/MissingPersons/Case#/87093?nav"^^xsd:String;
