  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "He was last seen by his son leaving his residence at 7 p.m. on May 1, 2007 in San Bruno, California. He left to pick up a fare for his private car service business the E-Limousine Services. He told his family that he had a fare at 7:30 p.m. There is no indication who he was supposed to pick up that evening or where. He has not been heard from since and his vehicle, a new 2007 black Lincoln Town Car has not been recovered. His cell phone and credit cards have not been used since that day."^^xsd:String;
