  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "Gustavo left his sisters residence with none of his personal belongings. He also left without his prescription medication. Family reported it was common for him to leave for a few days at a time, but he always returned. Family members attempted to make contact with him, but were unable to do so. Family members believed Gustavo may have traveled to the State of Washington."^^xsd:String;
