  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "On May 13, 2001, Geraldine Myers was last seen about 8:45 p.m. at her apartment at the 3700 Block of San Simeon Way in Riverside, California. One of her sons took her to church and to lunch at a local restaurant for Mother’s Day and another son took her to dinner, then dropped her off at her apartment. Evidence in the home suggested that Myers was murdered there, but her body was never located. Bailey Lamar Jackson Jr was convicted of robbing and murdering Myers and was sentenced to death."^^xsd:String;
  mpr:columnURI "https://www.namus.gov/MissingPersons/Case#/91443?nav"^^xsd:String;
