  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance """Source: Charley Project

Roof was last seen on April 15, 1994 leaving her mother's home in a mobile home park on east Avenue I in Los Angeles, California. She has never been heard from again. Foul play is suspected in Roof's disappearance due to her lifestyle and the people she associated with. Her case remains unsolved."""^^xsd:String;
