  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "Donald Rohrenbacher was last seen on March 18, 1994 in Los Angeles, California. He drove up Highway 39 to Valley of the Moon, parked his car and went for a hike into San Gabriel Canyon about 15 miles north of Azusa, California. His vehicle was located on Highway 39, San Gabriel Canyon. A week passed before he was reported missing, and no one knew where he had gone until his car was located."^^xsd:String;
