  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance """Nickolas was 54 years old when he was last seen driving a friend's car in Apple Valley back in 1993. The car was later recovered in Las Vegas; it had all of his property in it, including his false teeth. When the car was recovered, it was fully functional, no keys and had gas in it. 
He is described as a white male, 5'7\", 185 lbs, with brown eyes and brown/gray hair. He had scars on both feet from shrapnel."""^^xsd:String;
  mpr:columnURI "https://www.namus.gov/MissingPersons/Case#/2985?nav"^^xsd:String;
