  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "Kapusi was reported as missing by a friend that came from Switzerland looking for him on behalf of his family members in Hungary. The last time the friend had physically seen Kapusi was in 1993 in Palo Alto. The friend had feared that Kapusi may have been the victim of foul play while he was a resident of Mountain View over some business dealings, as Kapusi said he feared for his life and felt the need to leave the country in their last phone conversation in 1996."^^xsd:String;
