  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "He was last seen on April 30, 1992, in Los Angeles, California. He left his apartment on Country Club Drive near the Mid-City district with a group of friends to go looting on the second day of the 1992 Riots and never returned home."^^xsd:String;
