  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance """MP was last seen at his place of employment on 5/28/1991. He told his employer he was going to Texas to visit and assist an aging uncle. He left his vehicle and mechanics tools behind. He has not been seen or heard from since.
The sister of the mp told detectives the mp had no uncle in Texas and that he used concaine and was mentally unstable. It was not uncommon for him to leave for long periods of time, which is the reason he was not reported missing until 8/12/1991."""^^xsd:String;
  mpr:columnURI "https://www.namus.gov/MissingPersons/Case#/7848?nav"^^xsd:String;
