  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "Maria went on a vacation to Mexico with her husband and three children on 06-13-1990. They left their oldest son behind. Maria called her son on 06-23-1990 and stated the family was leaving Guadalajara, Mexico and heading to Manzanillo, Colima, Mexico. The husband and three children returned home on 06-28-1990. Maria's husband stated he was involved in an argument with Maria and she stormed off, never to be seen again."^^xsd:String;
  mpr:columnURI "https://www.namus.gov/MissingPersons/Case#/31113?nav"^^xsd:String;
  mpr:hasImageURL "https://www.namus.gov/api/CaseSets/NamUs/MissingPersons/Cases/31113/Images/40183/Thumbnail"^^xsd:String .

