  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "In April 1990 Mark Leese left port in Chinook Washington as a solo captain of a salmon fishing boat. On 05/30/1990 his boat was found shipwrecked in the Pacific Ocean, Point Reyes, adjacent to the Great Beach or Pt. Reyes Lighthouse. He was lost at sea and never seen again."^^xsd:String;
