  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "Angela was traveling across Canada from Ontario to Vancouver, BC. According to the Case file, Angela was hitchhiking by herself. She was to meet her parents in San Francisco, CA but never showed up. Postcards were received by family and friends up to Calgary, Alberta in August of 1983. Angela was born in the Bay Area and scheduled to attend college in Ontario, CA in September."^^xsd:String;
