  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "Brandi was 2 years old when she was last seen in Nipton, California on 10/07/1982. To date, Brandi has not been located. During the investigation, detectives uncovered information that Brandi may have been kidnapped and murdered. (H# 1983-008). Brandi is described as 2 1/2 feet tall, 32 pounds, with light brown shoulder length hair, and hazel eyes. She is believed to have been wearing a yellow jacket with hood. Several items that were missing when Brandi was taken were a stuffed learning teddy bear, a blue blanket with an embroidered yellow duck and a multicolored patchwork blanket."^^xsd:String;
