  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance """Kimberly Cozart (aka: Kimberly Harper) has been missing since February 1977. She was last known to be living on Banner Grade Road in Julian, California. She was reported missing by her sister on December 15, 1995. MP is the daughter of MP #18020 - Joyce HARPER. https://www.namus.gov/MissingPersons/Case#/18020

Kimberly Cozart is described as a 15-year old, White female. At the time of her disappearance she was 5’00” tall and weighed about 100 lbs. She had long reddish-brown hair and brown eyes."""^^xsd:String;
  mpr:columnURI "https://www.namus.gov/MissingPersons/Case#/29117?nav"^^xsd:String;
