  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "Packard was travelling with Linda Lovell hiking along the CA coast with a final destination of Spokane WA. Packard called his family on 6-10-1974 from Stinson Beach, CA. On 6-20-1974, a travelers check in Packard's name was cashed at a store in Westport, Mendocino County, CA. Linda Lovell and Stephen Packard have not been heard from since then."^^xsd:String;
  mpr:columnURI "https://www.namus.gov/MissingPersons/Case#/14418?nav"^^xsd:String;
  mpr:hasImageURL "https://www.namus.gov/api/CaseSets/NamUs/MissingPersons/Cases/14418/Images/26667/Thumbnail"^^xsd:String .

