  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance "Cynthia was last seen playing outside her apartment complex in San Jose, California. She has a cowlick on the right side of her hairline, a mole on the left side of her back, and a small cleft chin. Her eyes may appear dark blue to hazel in color. Cynthia was last seen wearing a red and white striped sleeveless shirt with a blue star on the front and purple pants. She was not wearing any footwear. Her nickname is Cindy."^^xsd:String;
