  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance """Wanda Loe was working at Sunnyside Restaurant and Lodge as a waitress in North Lake Tahoe, when she failed to show up for work and suddenly disappeared. It was also noted that she never picked up her last paycheck nor had picked up her mail for about three weeks. Area checks were made for any evidence of Wanda or her property. Negative results.

Wanda was last seen wearing unknown clothing description. Wears \"hippie round rimmed glasses\". No known scars/marks or tattoos."""^^xsd:String;
