  mpr:hasCircumstanceOfDisappearance """On the evening of 11/7/1960, Doris left her residence to go shopping at a local mall, then she was to go to a movie. She left the residence in her 1959, Mercury, CA plate SUR368, white. She was wearing a purple sweater, skirt, and blue hooded type coat. She was never seen or heard from again. 
On 11/10/1960, the family vehicle was discovered parked outside a beauty salon known to the victim, at 3331 Balmoral Drive."""^^xsd:String;
